overview: Three teams clash in an epic WarGames Cage Match. "Diamond" Dallas Page, "Rowdy" Roddy Piper & The Ultimate Warrior take on Hollywood Hogan, "The Hitman" Bret Hart & Stevie Ray as well as Kevin Nash, Sting & Lex Luger. Brothers collide when Rick Steiner faces Scott Steiner. Konnan goes one-on-one with Scott Hall. Dean Malenko takes on Curt Hennig and more!
title: WCW Fall Brawl 1998
